  "text": "Spacefilling curves, first introduced by Peano, Hilbert, and Sirpinski, have more recently come into use in solving routing and partitioning problems (c.f. Bartholdi and Platzman [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] ). Our description here will omit most technical details.",
